alerts.title: Special Weather Statement
alerts.description: ...Gusty Winds This Evening... The widespread rain will gave to scattered showers between 430 PM and 6 PM this evening, with more widespread showers expected to advance into the area after 8 PM. There will be brief intervals of gusty winds late this afternoon and evening, with a few gusts of 35 to 45 MPH possible. This may bring down small branches and cause loose light weight objects to blow around.
